<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再去打個招呼好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">似乎有新人搬到這座島上啦。<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經見過對方了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身負守護島嶼治安重任的我<delay frames="20" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定得先去好好地跟對方打個招呼啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好的開始，可是成功的一半咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糟啦！<delay frames="40" />
