<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙到底收到什麼會開心啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="013_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />終於到了這一天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
聽說<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那傢伙<delay20 />要離開這座島，<delay8 />
